			Profile
			
			




Prof.ZhaoobtainedhisB.Eng,M.EngandPhDdegreesfromZJUin1982,1985and1990respectively.HeJoinedtheDeptofMSE,ZJUin1985andstudiedinRWTHAachenfrom1987to1990.HewastheassociatedirectoroftheDeptfrom1993to1999andtheDeptdirectorfrom1999to2006.Hewaspromotedtofullprofessorin1995.HeispresentlytheQiushidistinguishedprofessorofZhejiangUniversity,directormemberofChineseMaterialsResearchSocietyandChineseRareEarthSociety,memberoftheExpertCommitteeofNSFCinMetallicMaterials,andtheeditor-in-chiefoftheJournalofMaterialsScienceandEngineering.
Prof.Zhao&rsquo;sresearchworksfocusmainlyonthermoelectricmaterialsincludingbismuthtellurideandsilverantimonygermaniumtelluridebasedhigh-performancethermoelectricnanocompositesandmagnesiumsilicidebasedenvironment-friendlythermoelectricmaterials,andlithium-ionbatterymaterials,especiallylithiumironphosphatecathodematerialsforlithium-ionpowerbatteries.Hehaspublishedmorethan200SCI-citedjournalpapers,andholdsmorethan20inventions.





			
				
			Researchwork
			
			Thermoelectricmaterials,Lithium-ionmaterials
			
				
